{
  "texts": [
    "HuatuoGPT will provide the answer to the question generated by the agents.",
    "MedCaptioner MedCaptioner (Xie et al., 2024) is a medical image captioner which can generate the caption without any query.",
    "Besides, it decomposes the image report into five parts, including the Modality Classification, Structure Detection, ROI Analysis, Leison Texture, and Local-global Relation.",
    "The structured report gives a comprehensive description and can help the agent to better understand the medical image.",
    "MiniCPM MiniCPM (Hu et al., 2024a) is the MLLM developed for general domains."
  ]
}